{
  "stem": "3638.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "His brother was the secretary of Amon Goeth.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Amon Goeth?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was the commander of the Plaszow concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was the most important person.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Bankier was the most important.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were quite a few important persons there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, that's right.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He had him because, because he-- Pemper, he, he was a very skilled man.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, nobody could do what-- he could talk to you, like you do, and at the same time writing on the machine, and, and no make mistakes.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He could have done it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But there could be there were some monkey business behind it, which we never know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was in Emalia until the time where I had to go to Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Until, I think, the end of '44.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Not quite end of '44.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I was there-- as soon as I went to Emalia-- first, we went from-- as you know-- from Emalia to, to ghetto every day.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then after, before the liquidation of the ghetto, we went from, from Plaszow to Emalia.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I believe that was-- I was taken before the liquidation.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Could be-- could be something like that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Could be, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Plaszow, I can't remember how long, but we-- but as soon, but as soon as Schindler saw that it's going to be difficult to bring us, we saw all the atrocities, and we didn't know what's going to happen.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he managed to build the barracks on Emalia, and then we came to Emalia, and we stay on Emalia.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that could be one and a half year.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not very long.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Could be, maybe, three months.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it doesn't take long to build wooden barracks.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, that's right.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Behind the factory.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Correct.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
